OL,3,CFlorist, cafe and hair salon destroyed
OL,4,Cby 'arsonists'
OL,6,FHelen Steel reports from the scene
OL,8,FPolice are investigating a suspected
OL,9,Farson attack which severely damaged
OL,10,Fthree businesses in Huddersfield.
OL,12,FFire swept through Kelly's Cafe,
OL,13,FYorkshire White Rose Florist and
OL,14,FDominoes hair salon, on St John's Road
OL,15,Fin Birkby, on Tuesday night.
OL,17,FCafe owner Kelly Hildreth said said
OL,18,Fthe incident had ruined "13 years of
OL,19,Fhard graft".
