OL,6,F"I'm absolutely gutted, it's all I've
OL,7,Fgot apart from my family this is it
OL,8,Fthis is what I've worked hard for,"
OL,9,Fshe said.
OL,11,F"No job, no income for Christmas. This
OL,12,Fis where we are."
OL,14,FShe said her daughter was among the
OL,15,Fstaff who had been left jobless.
OL,17,FIn a Facebook post, she added: "I'd
OL,18,Flike to apologise to all our customers
OL,19,Fand thank you for your business over
OL,20,Fthe years, it meant the world to me."
