OL,6,FThe owners of the hair salon told the
OL,7,FYorkshire Live website they were
OL,8,Funsure of the extent of the damage.
OL,10,FOne of them, named as Seona, said:
OL,11,F"We've been doing hairdressing for 40
OL,12,Fyears now and have been at this
OL,13,Flocation for 31 years. It's a long
OL,14,Ftime ."
OL,16,FShe added she was "just thankful that
OL,17,Fno one was in the premises at the
OL,18,Ftime", adding: "We've had wonderful,
OL,19,Fheartfelt messages from people sharing
OL,20,Flove and support."
